title: Pool de BNB e BUSD
body:
Portugues:
O que acham de ser possivel atraves da PancakeSwap fazer pool de BNB e BUSD?

Seria Optimo colocar os nossos BNB's e até mesmo BUSD a fazer pool tal e qual como a CAKE.


Ingles:
What do you think it is possible through PancakeSwap to pool BNB and BUSD?

It would be great to put our BNB's and BUSD to pool, just like we do with CAKE.
choices: Não me parece uma boa ideia!!! (Doesn't sound like a good idea to me!!!)
author: 0xb6f6681d33E49d1393b12D65326D49cde2A80253
